kt:DisclosureOfNotesOnFinancialResultsExplanatoryTextBlock contextRef="OneD">1. These financial results were reviewed and recommended by the Audit Committee and approved by the Board of Directors at their meetings held on August 14, 2025. These results are as per Regulation 33 of the SEBI (Listing Obligations and Disclosure Requirements) Regulations, 2015, as amended. The statutory auditors have carried out a limited review of these results for the quarter ended June 30, 2025 and have issued an unmodified report on these results. &lt;BR&gt; 
